window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Waking up doesn’t have to be an abrupt, jarring experience. Bram Barouh guides you in a meditation that walks you through that foggy territory between sleep and wakefulness, helping to ease you into the day feeling in tune with your mental state.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p> <p>Bram, a mindfulness educator, has a lighthearted nature and approachable wisdom that makes practicing meditation seem effortless. With his guidance, it’s never been easier to take part in a moment of positive thinking.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p> <p>Guided by leading experts and personalities in wellness, morning meditations are brief listens focused specifically on helping you start your day on the right foot. They don’t require any previous experience - they're easy to get into and designed to help you take a moment each morning to simply check in with yourself.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p> <p>This title is part of the Audible Sleep Collection, exclusive audio experiences created to help you fall asleep, stay asleep, and wake up in the right morning mindset. New and free for members.</p>"; 
